## Production Credentials to Obtain

### 1. Bakong KHQR (Real Production)
Apply at: **https://bakong.nbc.org.kh/**
- Contact NBC Cambodia for merchant credentials
- Sandbox: `yourname@devb` → Production: `yourstore@yourbank`

### 2. Top-up Provider (Real Games)
Options:
- **Codashop Reseller Program** — https://codashop.com/become-a-partner
- **UniPin Reseller** — https://unipin.com/business
- **Razer Gold** — https://razer.com/gold/merchants
- **Direct from publishers** (Garena, Moonton, etc.) — requires business registration

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Without a real reseller agreement, game credits cannot be delivered. The current code uses API placeholders. You MUST sign up with a provider before going live.
